WEBVTT

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:34.576
In fact, you'll be surprised to know
that males dress to impress the women,

00:03:34.600 --> 00:03:36.176
and I'll show you how.

00:03:36.200 --> 00:03:38.736
So here we have a long-tailed widowbird,

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:41.016
and this is how they would normally look.

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:43.456
But when it comes to the breeding season,

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.776
everything changes,

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:47.776
and this is how he looks.

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:49.096
(Audience murmurs)

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:50.360
Yeah?

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:54.976
Birds also, multiple species of them,

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:58.576
do love to touch and cuddle
just like humans.

00:03:58.600 --> 00:04:00.896
And I know you're
wondering about this one.